        {
            "title": "Welcome to WP Travel Engine 5.5",
            "content": [
                "WP Travel Engine 5.5 includes the most awaited and requested features, including enhancements and bug fixes.",
                "This page highlights the new features and resources for users to provide an understanding of those features.",
                "<a href=\"https://docs.wptravelengine.com/docs/wp-travel-engine-5-5/\" target=\"_blank\">View Latest Features</a>"
            ],
