        {
            "title": "Social Login",
            "content": [
                "Social Login features allows customers registration and log in to the site using facebook, Google and LinkedIn.",
                "This makes checkout process seamless and improves conversion. It also makes access to User Dashboard easy as customers don't need to remember another username and password.",
                "<a href=\"https://docs.wptravelengine.com/docs/social-login/\" target=\"_blank\">View Documentation</a>",
                "You have to enable social login to make this feature available to the end-user."
            ],
