        {
            "title": "Related Trips",
            "content": [
                "Since WP Travel Engine 5.5, there is an option to show and hide related trips for Single Trip, which is enabled in default.",
                "<a href=\"https://docs.wptravelengine.com/docs/wp-travel-engine-5-5/#3-toc-title\" target=\"_blank\">View Documentation</a>",
                "You can add related trips from Display Settings."
            ],
            "images": [
                {
                    "src": "%assets_path_url%related-trip-settings.png",
                    "caption": "Related Trip Settings"
                }
            ],
            "classNames": [],
            "attributes": {
                "style": "margin-bottom:32px;"
            }
        },
        {
            "title": "Trip Taxes",
            "content": [
                "This feature allows you to add tax for the trips.",
                "<a href=\"https://docs.wptravelengine.com/docs/wp-travel-engine-5-5/#0-toc-title\" target=\"_blank\">View Documentation</a>",
                "To use the feature, Tax should be enabled and configured."
            ],
            "images": [
                {
                    "src": "%assets_path_url%tax-settings.png",
