            }
        },
        {
            "title": "Hourly Tours",
            "content": [
                "WP Travel Engine 5.5 now provides an hourly booking feature for tours/activities that are in hours, not days. Now, you can add multiple hour slots for each day and week.",
                "<a href=\"https://docs.wptravelengine.com/docs/wp-travel-engine-5-5/#1-toc-title\" target=\"_blank\">View Documentation</a>",
                "To enable the hourly feature, make sure you have select the duration type as hours."
            ],
